<br>
Anyone have any knew thoughts on this upcoming Expansion.<br>
<br>
They are being more vague on this expansion than others that I have been around for. They have touched up on a few spells and on Item Augmentation that I like.<br>
<br>
They have not writen of any new AA abilities. I am hoping they do throw out some New AA. If anything if anyone has some nice links to rumors,news etc. <br>
<br>
They have the release date &quot;set&quot; for under a month away. Would like to see more opinions and how you feel this will effect EQ.<br>
<br>
They made some &quot;raid&quot; content max of 36. While its larger than the first &quot;vision&quot; for this expansion. I think its actually worse for high end guilds. Who have been forced to increase their roster size to compete in highend POP. It was one thing to be a one group expansion, its another to have 50-60 people on wanting some raiding action and telling many of them better luck next.<br>
<br>
While the argument could be made that you just do two 36 raids, and this is semi valid. It doesnt take into effect class number balance. <br>
